CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 14 and 15, reads: "Activities Week at Pittsburgh's Y.M.C.A. - ...Lower shots (l to r,) show booths of business men who exhibited in 'Y' lobby, Scott Service Garage, La Salle Beauty School and Bob West's Service Garage. Scott's booth held a prize drawing contest that was won by champion Joe Louis. (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Scotty's Service Garage and Esso Station booth, with two women seated behind tables, at Centre Avenue YMCA
